  "functional": {
    "latex": "8\\,\\beta_0 + 11\\,\\beta_1 + 13\\,\\beta_2 + 3\\,\\beta_1\\beta_2",
    "value": 35
  },
  "solution": {
    "answer": "$H_0 \\cong \\mathbb{Z},\\quad H_1 \\cong \\mathbb{Z},\\quad H_2 \\cong \\mathbb{Z},\\quad H_n = 0 \\text{ for } n \\geq 3.$",
    "steps": [
      "For any spaces $X, Y$ with a common basepoint, $\\tilde{H}_n(X \\vee Y) \\cong \\tilde{H}_n(X) \\oplus \\tilde{H}_n(Y)$.",
      "$\\tilde{H}_*(S^1)$: $\\tilde{H}_1 = \\mathbb{Z}$, all other reduced groups $= 0$.",
      "$\\tilde{H}_*(S^2)$: $\\tilde{H}_2 = \\mathbb{Z}$, all other reduced groups $= 0$.",
      "Adding: $\\tilde{H}_1(S^1 \\vee S^2) = \\mathbb{Z}$ (from $S^1$) and $\\tilde{H}_2(S^1 \\vee S^2) = \\mathbb{Z}$ (from $S^2$).",
      "Restoring $H_0 = \\tilde{H}_0 \\oplus \\mathbb{Z} = \\mathbb{Z}$. All higher groups vanish."
    ]
  }
}
